text: Another observation about Don't Look Up. Like It's a Mad, Mad, Mad, Mad, Mad World it assembles a huge number of famous-for-the-day stars. The cast of IAMMMMMW included: Spencer Tracy, Edie Adams, Milton Berle, Sid Caesar, Buddy Hackett, Ethel Merman, Dorothy Provine, Mickey Rooney, Dick Shawn, Phil Silvers, Terry-Thomas, and Jonathan Winters.
